#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced usage"
msgstr "Uso avanzado"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remote controlling and scripting via &DBus;"
msgstr "Control remoto e uso de guións mediante &DBus;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can control &kmix; via &DBus;. This is for advanced users who want to "
"achieve special tasks, like muting the PC every day at 10 pm, or for any "
"other scripting task."
msgstr ""
"Pode controlar &kmix; mediante &DBus;. Isto permite a usuarios avanzados "
"realizar tarefas especiais como silenciar o computador todos os días ás dez "
"da tarde, ou calquera outra tarefa a efectuar mediante scripts."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid "List all &kmix; related &DBus; methods and properties"
msgstr ""
"Para listar todos os métodos e propiedades de &DBus; relacionados con &kmix;:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid "qdbus org.kde.kmix"
msgstr "qdbus org.kde.kmix"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid "Getting volume level (0-100%):"
msgstr "Para obter o volume (0-100%):"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"qdbus org.kde.kmix /Mixers/0/Master_0 org.freedesktop.DBus.Properties.Get "
"org.kde.KMix.Control volume"
msgstr ""
"qdbus org.kde.kmix /Mixers/0/Master_0 org.freedesktop.DBus.Properties.Get "
"org.kde.KMix.Control volume"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting volume level (0-100%):"
msgstr "Para cambiar o volume (0-100%):"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"qdbus org.kde.kmix /Mixers/0/Master_0 org.freedesktop.DBus.Properties.Set "
"org.kde.KMix.Control volume 70"
msgstr ""
"qdbus org.kde.kmix /Mixers/0/Master_0 org.freedesktop.DBus.Properties.Set "
"org.kde.KMix.Control volume 70"

